properties.Text: How to Play: Traverse North America as you answer questions about history and geography. Click on the map to go to the country selection and answer questions. Each question presented to you is worth 1 point, once you get 15 points in a country, it will add to your total countries visited. Travel North America to answer more questions, revisit countries for even more points, and get many points to become a true voyager!
